window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>How do you go from blind date to shotgun wedding in a single afternoon?</b></p> <p>You catch the eye of a man like Maximo Leonotti, that's how.</p> <p>It's not like he had to force me. I was hooked on the stormy-eyed stranger from the moment we met… right up until I felt the pinch in my arm.</p> <p>The next thing I know, I'm waking up on his private jet, halfway to Las Vegas. Apparently, for an impromptu wedding. Our wedding.</p> <p>That's when the panic sets in. This can't be happening. I'm Elira Përmeti, daughter of Afrim, leader of the Albanian mafia. If I go missing, all hell will break loose.</p> <p>But when I tell Maximo, he just smiles. Turns out, he already knows all of my secrets, and now it's time I hear one of his:</p> <p>My father owes him a debt, and I'm the payment.</p> <p>Devil's Lily <i>is a standalone, dual pov dark mafia romance featuring a possessive, 'touch her and I'll unalive you' type anti-hero and a feisty, smart heroine. No OW drama, no cliffhanger, and a hard-won HEA.</i></p>"; 
